OL,3,CWhat is Plato - the operation declared
OL,4,Cafter stabbing at Manchester synagogue?
OL,6,FTwo people have died and a suspect has
OL,7,Fbeen shot dead by police following an
OL,8,Fattack outside a synagogue in
OL,9,FManchester.
OL,11,FThe incident on Thursday prompted
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) to
OL,13,Fdeclare Operation Plato - the national
OL,14,Fcode-word used by police and emergency
OL,15,Fservices when responding to a
OL,16,F"marauding terror attack".
