OL,3,CWhat is Plato - the operation declared
OL,4,Cafter stabbing at Manchester synagogue?
OL,6,FThe attack came as members of the
OL,7,FJewish community observe Yom Kippur `
OL,8,Fthe holiest day in the Jewish
OL,9,Fcalendar, and it is a time when
OL,10,Fsynagogues are usually particularly
OL,11,Fbusy.
OL,13,FThe operation was initiated after
OL,14,Fpolice were called to Heaton Park
OL,15,FHebrew Congregation Synagogue in
OL,16,FCrumpsall after a member of the public
OL,17,Fsaw a car being driven towards people
OL,18,Fand one man being stabbed.
OL,20,FBut what is Operation Plato, and why
OL,21,Fwas it declared in Manchester?
