OL,11,FWhat is Operation Plato?
OL,13,FOperation Plato refers to a code name
OL,14,Fused by police and emergency services
OL,15,Fin response to any fast-moving attack,
OL,16,Ftypically involving dangerous weapons,
OL,17,Fand is known as a "marauding terror
OL,18,Fattack" or MTA.
