OL,3,CWhat is Plato - the operation declared
OL,4,Cafter stabbing at Manchester synagogue?
OL,6,FPlato follows a set of agreed
OL,7,Fprinciples carried out by multiple
OL,8,Fagencies, including police, ambulance,
OL,9,Fand fire services, under the Joint
OL,10,FOperating Principles (JOPs).
OL,12,FIt is designed for those agencies to
OL,13,Fcoordinate their response to address
OL,14,Fserious threats quickly using JOPs
OL,15,Fdeveloped by the Home Office and the
OL,16,Femergency services community.
