OL,16,FWhy was Plato declared in Manchester?
OL,18,FPolice declared Plato following the
OL,19,Fstabbing at Heaton Park Hebrew
OL,20,FCongregation Synagogue on Thursday,
OL,21,Fafter it met the criteria for an MTA.
