OL,3,CWhat is Plato - the operation declared
OL,4,Cafter stabbing at Manchester synagogue?
OL,6,FThe incident involved a vehicle being
OL,7,Fdriven into a crowd, multiple
OL,8,Fstabbings near the synagogue, and
OL,9,Fmembers of the public being injured -
OL,10,Fall of which meet the criteria for a
OL,11,FPlato response.
OL,13,FThe incident has also prompted Prime
OL,14,FMinister Keir Starmer to fly home
OL,15,Fearly from a meeting of European
OL,16,Fleaders to chair an emergency Cobra
OL,17,Fmeeting following the attack.
